{"tid":1324553,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"槍口對外呀咁多位！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-16T15:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T16:06:52.000Z","uid":92558,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"be503de89a96880a90e083b149995c16232ac784","tid":1324553,"uid":92558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:01:56.000Z","msg":"做咩今日推上熱門既全部都係分化po<br />\n屌完朱凱迪屌社工再屌林卓廷<br />\n隔離po都有話啦 中共最叻玩輿論戰 依加比人帶梗風向呀傻9<br />\n當初講咗唔分化唔割蓆唔篤灰呀 槍口要一致對外<br />\n對準政府中共黑警藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比啲1毛分化到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n清算呢啲贏咗先慢慢清啦<br />\n認清敵人呀咁多位<br />\n要贏！一齊黎一齊走<br />\n兄弟爬山"},{"pid":"7f99ae1d14ab1865ca08e7757312c2629a612b6c","tid":1324553,"uid":92558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ead8e242fc1c2ab5dfbc2267ee91b6c9b23babc","tid":1324553,"uid":92558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:03:31.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a5990587b05371ab76dd26ccdf6811b1be24e8","tid":1324553,"uid":92558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5e29a5d0f04dcff93f2f04d4b056aa4a9525c67f","tid":1324553,"uid":198822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6bd52999778fdfd6ceb4e7d2a959d9aea3923e9a","tid":1324553,"uid":110018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"勿分化 勿割蓆"},{"pid":"851f42156a8fb60328f8088c76fcdb72bcdaf3ad","tid":1324553,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2c0e0f